Package rfid.rfcode

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Channel
    Represents the Channel objects that each reader has.
    Constants
    Holds important constants to be used between classes.
    HttpParameter
    Represents an HTTP parameter to be passed in an HTTP request.
    HttpRequest
    Represents an HTTP request to be used to access the Zone Manager API.
    Reader
    Represents physical Reader objects.
    Tag
    Represents physical Tag objects.
    TagLink
    Represents an open connection between a Tag object and a Channel object.
    ZMSystem
    Maintains ArrayLists of readers and tags through which all components of the RFID hardware can be accessed.
